"Tabs/indentation
    set tabstop=4 "width of tab character
    set softtabstop=0 "zero prevents tab character
    set expandtab "tab key inserts spaces instead of tab characters, in insert mode
    set shiftwidth=4 "width of an indent
    set smarttab "tab key intelligently inserts whitespace to align to the above widths

"Show whitespace
    set listchars+=lead:⋅,trail:⋅ "use dot to show leading/trailing spaces
    "set list "disabled by default
